description: Chase and Cole are looking better than ever! Playing around with water balloons and getting wet, all while wearing white t-shirts, was just too much for us to handle. It didn’t take them long to just drop everything and get right down to it! Chase grabbed Cole’s hand and led him inside, “Alright, let’s go!” The cute, willing bottom followed happily, and got exactly what he wanted…a good pounding he won’t soon forget!
title: Chase & Cole: Bareback
